@startuml

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888
hide empty members

title Template Method Pattern - CaffeineBeverage

abstract class CaffeineBeverage {
    +prepareRecipe() : void <<final>>
    #boilWater() : void
    #pourInCup() : void
    #{abstract} brew() : void
    #{abstract} addCondiments() : void
}

class Coffee extends CaffeineBeverage {
    #brew() : void
    #addCondiments() : void
}

class Tea extends CaffeineBeverage {
    #brew() : void
    #addCondiments() : void
}

note right of CaffeineBeverage
  <b>AbstractClass</b>
  --
  <b>prepareRecipe()</b> = Template Method
    final로 선언, 알고리즘 골격 고정
    1. boilWater()       (공통)
    2. brew()            (가변, abstract)
    3. pourInCup()       (공통)
    4. addCondiments()   (가변, abstract)
  --
  boilWater, pourInCup = Concrete Operation
  brew, addCondiments  = Primitive Operation
end note

note bottom of Coffee
  <b>ConcreteClass</b>
  brew()          → 필터로 커피 추출
  addCondiments() → 설탕, 우유
end note

note bottom of Tea
  <b>ConcreteClass</b>
  brew()          → 티백 우리기
  addCondiments() → 레몬
end note

@enduml